collection.name: Non-Fungible People by Daz 3D
collection.description:
Airdrop coming on June 15th in partnership with Clinique!

All NFP holders will be eligible for an NFPet coming soon! (Free + Gas) 
You can also upgrade your pet to one of 11 different dog breeds with outfits, accessories and more! Deets in Discord.
Personalizations, Animations and more are available to show of your NFP! 
To update your OpenSea image go to https://nfp.daz3d.com/nfp/dashboard

Daz 3D’s debut NFT collection, Non-Fungible People (NFP), is a collection of 8,888 women and non-binary hyper-realistic 3D Avatars.  Each NFP comes with a fully rigged 3D model and a PFP rendered in breathtaking 3D.  Use your NFP for video calls, motion capture, game design, animation and more!

You can even upgrade your NFP with a new wearable from the [Champion x NFP Collection](https://opensea.io/collection/champion-x-non-fungible-people)

License: All NFP’s come with the Daz 3D interactive license found here: https://www.daz3d.com/eula
